				<ANNOTATION_VALUE>hot men nokh im aroysgenumen er zol oyfroymen di toyte, ir farshteyt, s'geven a sakh toyte gehargete, m'darf men oyfroymen,</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
				</ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION>
